AIIMS Kalyani Recruitment 2025 - Apply Online for 150 Senior Resident Posts
Prasanna / All Government Jobs / Aug 25, 2025, 15:10 IST
 All India Institute of Medical Science
 150 Jobs |  Posted On : 25-Aug-2025 |  West Bengal |  Salary : 15,600 to 39,100




FOLLOW

All India Institute of Medical Sciences (AIIMS) Kalyani has announced the offcial notification for 2025. To fill up the vacancies for 150 Senior Resident Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the MD/ MS, DNB, and Post-Graduation can grab this chance and apply for the AIIMS Kalyani Recruitment 2025. Here we include the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts. Interested and eligible candidates can apply online through the website on or before the last date of application.




If you are looking for more, here is a list of Government Jobs in 2025 that you can all apply for. Use this link for more jobs in West Bengal.

AIIMS Kalyani Recruitment 2025 - Eligibility Criteria
Name of the Posts	No.of Vacancies	Qualification
Senior Resident 	150	MD/ MS, DNB, Post Graduation

Age Limit for the AIIMS Kalyani Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Age Limit: 21 years.
The Maximum Age Limit: 45 years.
Age Relaxation is applicable as per norms.

Selection Process for the AIIMS Kalyani Recruitment 2025

Interview

Salay Structure for the AIIMS Kalyani Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Salary: Rs. 15,600 /- per month.
The Maximum Salary: Rs. 39,100 /- per month.

Application fee for the AIIMS Kalyani Recruitment 2025

Unreserved/OBC/EWS Candidates: Rs. 1000/-
SC/ ST Candidates: Nil
How to Apply for the AIIMS Kalyani Recruitment 2025
Visit the official website.
Go to the recruitment or career page.
Check for the Senior Resident Jobs 2025.
Read the notification carefully.
Check the eligibility criteria.
If you meet the eligibility criteria.
Click on the Apply Online link.
Fill out the given details carefully.
Pay the application fee (if applicable).
Submit the application form and capture the application number for further reference.

Important Dates

Starting Date of Application	19-08-2025
Last Date of Application	28-08-2025
